    "causal_summary": "The unified router refactor is not a router rewrite — it is a shadow compiler plus additive semantic gates whose entire safety model rests on content-addressed identity: a request pins one `effectivePolicyHash`, replay recompiles to byte-identical policy bodies, and rollback swaps to a byte-identical prior manifest [synthesis §1, §9]",
